quran[51]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,Twaa Syn Mym
  26,2,Tsino ni tsinyaali tsie shitabu shinoosinjia
  26,3,Kakhaba kario weyira omwene shichila mbu shibaba Abasuubili tawe
  26,4,"Ne khwenyanga khwakhabeshilie okhurula hekulu amangalimwa, mana amakosi kabu kehotselesilia amangalimwa ako"
  26,5,Ne nibuboolela obwitsulisio obuyiakha okhurula khu munji wetsimbabaasi beretsanga ehale ninabo
  26,6,"Toto bo bamala okhuyingasia, kholaano ahambi hano balanyoola amacheni kakalia kabakholelanga emibayo"
  26,7,"Koo, shibalolangakhwo liloba, ni emimela chinga chia khwamesiamwo, chia buli imbia indayi"
  26,8,"Toto mu ako khulimwo nende ameeko, halali abanji mubo shinibokhusuubila tawe"
  26,9,"Netoto Nyasaye wuwo, niye Owamani, Owetsimbabaasi muno"
  26,10,"Ne olwa Nyasaye wuwo yalaanga Musa, namuboolela mbu; “Tsia khubandu balia abamabii”"
  26,11,Abandu ba Firauni; (ubaboolele mbu) “Koo shimuritsanga Nyasaye tawe?”
  26,12,(Musa) Naboola’; mbu “Nyasaye wanje esie eritsanga baletsa okhuyingasia tawe.”
  26,13,"Ne eshilifu shianje shilola obuliro, ne olulimi lwanje shilurumbulanga obulayi tawe, kho yilila (Oburume buno) khu Haruni"
  26,14,"Nabo bali nende likhobo khwisie, kho eritsanga mbu balanzira"
  26,15,"Naboola; “Shikalikario tawe, kho mutsie nende amangalimwa kanje, toto efwe khuli halala ninanyu khuwulilanga.”"
  26,16,Kho mutsie khu Firauni mumuboolele mbu; “Toto efwe khuli Abarumwa ba Nyasaye webiloonje bioosi .”
  26,17,Mbu olekhule halala ninafu Abana ba Isarail
  26,18,"Naboola mbu; “koo, shikhwakhulela ewefu noli omwana, ne niwikhala mwifwe emika cholubaka lulwo?”"
  26,19,Ne nokhola eshikhole shishio shilia shawakhola ne noba mubalia abalakhupanga orio tawe
  26,20,"(Musa) naboola mbu; “Ndakhola ako, olwandali nendi mubandu balia abakora”"
  26,21,"“Mana nebelukha olwandali nebarire, ne Nyasaye wanje yambeele laano obwami ne yakholele okhuba Mubarumwa.”"
  26,22,"Ne obo nibo obulayi bwawumborolanga obwawakholela, newara Abana ba Israil mubusandi"
  26,23,Firauni naboola mbu; “Ne ni wina oyo Nyasaye weshialo shiosi?”
  26,24,(Musa) Naboola mbu; “ Nyasaye Omulesi owaloonga likulu nende eshialo nende ebili hakari wabio toto nimuli abokhukhaaba abwatoto.”
  26,25,"(Firauni) Naboolela balia abali nibamubotokhane mumbeka wuwe mbu: “koo! Shimuwulilanga tawe?”"
  26,26,(Musa) naboola mbu; “Nyasaye wenyu nende Nyasaye wa bapapa benyu abaranjilila.”
  26,27,(Firauni) Naboola mbu; “Toto bwene Omurumwa wenyu owabaruma enywe ni omulalu”
  26,28,"(Musa) Naboola mbu; “Niye Nyasaye webukwe nende Mumbo nende ebili hakari wabio, toto enywe nimuli abamanyanga"
  26,29,(Firauni) naboola mbu; “Niwitsa okhusuubila Nyasaye wundi ulali esie tawe toto nditsa okhukhola obe mubaboye.”
  26,30,Naboola; “Koo! Kata nekhurerera eshindu shili mubwang’angu?”
  26,31,"Naboola mbu; “Nakhashirerekhwo, toto noli mubandu baboolanga obwatoto.”"
  26,32,"Mana nasukuna indambushi yiyie, mana nikalukhana inzokha ilolekha"
  26,33,"Ne narusia omukhono kukwe, mana nikuba omulafu tswe khubakuhenga"
  26,34,"(Firauni) naboola okhuboolela abakhongo balia abamubotokhana mbu, “Toto uno ni omulosi umanyile muno”"
  26,35,"“Yenya okhubarusia mushialo shienyu nende obulosi bubwe, kho muboola murie?”"
  26,36,"Nibaboola mbu; “Mwehelesie ebise ye nende omusiani wabu, ne omure mwitokho habandu abakhung’asinjia Abandu”"
  26,37,Balakhurerera buli omulosi omukhongo umanyile muno
  26,38,Mana nibakhung’asia Abalosi khubise nende inyanga imanyikhane
  26,39,Ne Abandu nibaboolelwa mbu “Mumalile okhukhung’ana?”
  26,40,“Khwakhaba khurio khwaloonda kabalosi nikali mbu nibo balashila”
  26,41,"Kho mana Abalosi shingala boola, nibaboolela Firauni mbu; Koo, khulanyoola omurungo nikaba mbu nefwe khushila?”"
  26,42,"Naboola mbu; “eeh, ne khandi mwitsa okhuba mubalia abenjisibwa.”"
  26,43,Musa nababoolela mbu; “sukune ebiamwenya okhusukuna”
  26,44,"Nibasukuna emikoye chiabu nende tsindabushi tsiabu, nenibaboola mbu; “khumaani ka Firauni efwesa toto nefwe khulashila”"
  26,45,"Mana Musa nasukuna indabushi yiyie, mana niimilaa bioosi biabachikhanga"
  26,46,Awo abalosi nibakalukhana nibenama nibasujuda
  26,47,Nibaboola mbu; “khusuubile Nyasaye webiloonje bioosi
  26,48,Nyasaye wa Musa nende Haruni.”
  26,49,"(Firauni) naboola mbu; “Mumusuubile neshili okhubasubula, toto ye niye Omukhongo wenyu owabechesia obulosi. Kho mwitsa okhulola, Nditsa toto okhuteta emikhono chienyu nende ebilenje bienyu buchikha, ne nditsa okhubabamba mwesi”"
  26,50,"Nibaboola mbu; “obubii bubulaho, toto efwe khwitsa okhukalukha khu Nyasaye wefu”"
  26,51,"“Toto efwe khusuubile mbu Nyasaye wefu alakhuleshela tsimbi tsiefu, shichila efwe khubeele bokhuranjilila okhusuubila”"